line_1: Tho' wanton Love the breast embroil
line_2: Who would not pleas'd pursue the toil,

line_1: Or, should Despotic Rage the World embroil,
line_2: And bade the fervent City glow with Toil;

line_1: Or, should Despotic Rage the World embroil,
line_2: Join Land to Land, and marry Soil to Soil,

line_1: Or, should Despotic Rage the World embroil,
line_2: Unite the Poles, and without bloody Spoil
